The Mike Rosen Radio Show OCT-08-2014 WED

Posted Wednesday, October 8th 2014 @ 5pm

01pm - 03pm 10-08-2014

3. Mike deconstructs a letter to the editor on Jeffco. 

4. Panetta and Obama feud. 

5. Mike gets into the Matt Prater affair. 

6. Mike talks about Proposition 104. 

7. Christopher Kelly, author of,
    "America Invades: How We've Invaded or been Militarily Involved
